  "description": "Lo-fi hip hop tape machine — the short reel and heavy oxide push every note into cassette warmth. Minimal source input (12% mix) means the tape artifacts are the instrument; the signal is just an excuse for the saturation to happen. Gentle wow adds the human tremor that DAW quantization removes.",
